    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genus of two species of North and South America, one of which lives only on the Channel Islands off the California coast.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
